    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence and the controls in place. Validation evidence demonstrates RHI prediction error below the 10 % acceptance threshold across all 5 COU operating points. The solver build used for validation (ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2) is considered by the modelling team to be effectively equivalent to the production release (ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7) based on change-log review; accordingly, the credibility assessment is accepted without re-execution of validation under the production build.",
